# Smart Kitchen Safety System

## Overview
An IoT-based kitchen safety system that monitors environmental conditions and provides automated safety responses using cloud communication. :contentReference[oaicite:5]{index=5}

---

## Features
- Gas/temperature monitoring
- Cloud connectivity (MQTT/Blynk)
- Automated safety actions
- Remote monitoring

---

## Concepts
- IoT architecture (Device → Cloud)
- MQTT protocol
- Telemetry & control systems

---

## Components
- ESP32
- Sensors (Gas/Temp)
- Relay Module
- OLED Display

---

## Working
- Sensors collect data
- Data sent to cloud
- Alerts/actions triggered

---

## Applications
- Smart homes
- Industrial kitchens
- Safety monitoring systems

---
